 "2025-07-03T16:15:15.567827+00:00"}, {"role": "user", "content": "yes", "timestamp": "2025-07-03T16:15:28.460062+00:00"}, {"role": "coach", "content": "Here's the cool part - you're not just one thing. You might be a Warrior with your health, a Wealth Architect with money, and a Loving Partner in relationships. We're going to create a bunch of different Identities that represent these different parts of you. Pretty wild concept, right?", "timestamp": "2025-07-03T16:15:29.901649+00:00"}, {"role": "user", "content": "yes", "timestamp": "2025-07-03T16:15:41.397434+00:00"}, {"role": "coach", "content": "And here's how it works day-to-day. Instead of forcing yourself through tasks, you just ask 'Who needs to handle this?' Then you step into that identity. So if you need to tackle your budget, you don't struggle with it - you let your Wealth Architect handle it. Makes sense when you think about it that way.", "timestamp": "2025-07-03T16:15:43.792138+00:00"}, {"role": "user", "content": "haha ok", "timestamp": "2025-07-03T16:16:00.760194+00:00"}, {"role": "coach", "content": "So that's the basic idea. We'll go through some different exercises together to explore your different Identities, and refine them until they feel just right. It's creative and fun, not analytical.\\n\\nReady to dive in?", "timestamp": "2025-07-03T16:16:03.575647+00:00"}, {"role": "user", "content": "yes", "timestamp": "2025-07-03T16:16:09.417035+00:00"}, {"role": "coach", "content": "Wonderful! I'm excited to dive deeper with you. Before we get into the actual Identity work, I'd love to get to know you better. The more I understand about you and your world, the better I can help. So let's chat - I'll ask you some questions, and you can share as much or as little as feels right. Sound good?", "timestamp": "2025-07-03T16:16:11.341170+00:00"}, {"role": "user", "content": "ok", "timestamp": "2025-07-03T16:17:13.858523+00:00"}, {"role": "coach", "content": "Great! Let's start with something simple. Where